## Refund Order
---
##### Input Paramete

- Order ID(string)

#### Methods
```

order.refund(
    order_id
)
```

### Response

#### Success Response
```
{
    "status": true,
    "message": "Refund has been initiated"
}
```
#### Error Response 
```
{
    "status": false,
    "error": {
        "message": "error message here",
        "code": 204
    }
}
```

